18 The Telewar Menu (first menu heading
19 from the left offers four possible menu
20 selections.
21            River Meadow
23            Marshland Bog
24            Desert Dunes
25            Exit TeleWar
26
27 The first three selection will allow
28 you to play the indicated Battlefield
29 Map.  After choosing these selections, it
30 may take a few moments to load in the
31 requested game graphics.  It is
32 imperative that, when teleconnected to
33 another computer, both computers are
34 playing the same Battlefield Map!
35
36 Exit TeleWar will cause the TeleWar
37 program to end, de-allocating all memory
38 and resources that had been allocated.
39
40 When any of the TeleWar menu items have
41 been selected, the chime will sound and
42 the verification requester will be
43 displayed.

